data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION!! INVESTOR OPPORTUNITY OR FIRST TIME HOME BUYER!! Lovely spacious 2/2 ''VILLA'' all Ages Community.  Roofs replaced by the community in 2022. A/C 2021 and Water Heater 2023.  Villa with two patios. Laundry room with extra storage, unit also offers a carport. Association fee covers roofs maintenance, pest control, landscaping, cable, common areas, exterior insurance. Pet friendly community.  No Rental Restriction. Centrally located, near excellent schools, shopping, restaurants, & highways. Don't Miss out on this Great Opportunity. MUST SEE!!
